1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Scheme.

2
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,500
Half a year ago,

3
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:09,420
Eunuch Qin sent someone to see me.

4
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,160
He said

5
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:11,560
he took a fancy to Baoyue Pavilion's reputation

6
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,200
and wanted to run it behind the scenes,

7
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,800
but I refused him every time.

8
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:15,880
Since then,

9
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,880
girls have inexplicably gone missing.

10
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,080
But when they were found,

11
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:22,410
they were already dead,

12
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,960
and in a terrible state.

13
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:26,920
They must have been sent to Jile Palace to be tortured.

14
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,039
These beasts

15
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:30,420
should be cut into a thousand pieces.

16
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:33,580
Axiu also went missing suddenly.

17
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:35,600
I was afraid she would suffer the same fate,

18
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:37,259
so I hurriedly looked for her.

19
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,759
But when Eunuch Qin found out,

20
00:01:38,759 --> 00:01:40,960
he sent someone to tell me he could help.

21
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,440
So,

22
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:45,259
I guessed he must have harmed her.

23
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:47,759
But he had Consort De backing him,

24
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:49,360
so he had nothing to fear.

25
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,960
We couldn't resist.

26
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:52,759
So you had to compromise.

27
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:55,680
My original intention was to hand over Baoyue Pavilion

28
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,640
to rescue Xiu.

29
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,000
He agreed on the surface,

30
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:00,560
but then...

31
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,240
Let her go.

32
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,800
I have to say,

33
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:19,760
Miss Chai is a smart person.

34
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:42,040
If it weren't for you two,

35
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:44,560
I would have been doomed.

36
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,600
Especially Mr. Liu,

37
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:50,240
whom I almost misunderstood.

38
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,160
Unfortunately, regarding the Jile Palace,

39
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,720
someone is seeking justice for it,

40
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,560
and even Baoyue Tower will belong to him.

41
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,890
It's truly despicable.

42
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,760
This will be an antique someday.

43
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:01,160
It'd be a pity to break it.

44
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:03,240
Axiu's fate is still unknown.

45
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:05,360
Through this incident,

46
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,080
I discovered that

47
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:06,540
eunuchs

48
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,880
not only have desires like normal men,

49
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:09,640
but due to their physical defects,

50
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,360
they have a strong psychological need to compensate,

51
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,560
so their desires are even stronger.

52
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,220
Then Eunuch Qin

53
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:17,240
is using the eunuchs' desire for women

54
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,200
to satisfy his own greed for money.

55
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:24,020
But I think there's something he's more interested in.

56
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,100
You mean the regrowth.

57
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,680
I thought you didn't believe in it.

58
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,720
Of course I don't.

59
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,560
But he might.

60
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,890
He is rich and powerful.

61
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,940
According to psychology,

62
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:34,760
when someone reaches his level,

63
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,840
he will definitely try every means

64
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,240
to make up for his defect.

65
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,480
His defect is

66
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,600
not being able to be a normal man.

67
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,320
Axiu is the only one besides the deceased

68
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:45,120
who has witnessed the regrowth.

69
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:47,160
And she is very close to Eunuch Qiao.

70
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,760
If she falls into Eunuch Qin's hands,

71
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,480
he will definitely get to the bottom of it.

72
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:51,280
So,

73
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,040
that is why Axiu

74
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:54,560
is not in Jile Palace.

75
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,800
In that case,

76
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,810
Axiu should still be alive.

77
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,160
Once he finds out the truth,

78
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,240
whether it's true or false,

79
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,240
Eunuch Qin will not keep Axiu alive.

80
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,290
Is there any way to save her?

81
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,960
Those two scrolls,

82
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,760
did you find out who made them?

83
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,400
The one who drew those pictures is a scholar,

84
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:12,920
named Wang.

85
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,040
He lives outside the city.

86
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:15,400
He has already been brought in for questioning.

87
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,240
Not bad.

88
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,279
That was fast.

89
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,810
As expected of a constable.

90
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:22,120
Sir.

91
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,760
Something happened.

92
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:28,920
Has the identity of the deceased been confirmed?

93
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,880
The deceased was a scholar named Wang.

94
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:33,010
Let's start the autopsy immediately.

95
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,280
Here, this is for you.

96
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:52,280
Initial assessment.

97
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:54,409
The time of death was over 72 hours ago.

98
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,880
It is in the mid-stage of decomposition.

99
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:58,880
The body is showing signs of postmortem bloat.

100
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:01,040
A large amount of fluid has appeared on the skin.

101
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:03,280
It is filled with putrefactive gases and fluids.

102
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:05,340
The entire corpse has begun to swell.

103
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,490
The face is bloated.

104
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,720
The tongue is protruding.

105
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:10,120
There are numerous maggots around the eyes, mouth, and nose.

106
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:12,320
Skin peeling off from the distal limbs.

107
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,420
Help me turn the body over.

108
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,240
Found it.

109
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:22,800
The fatal wound

110
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,080
is here.

111
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,520
Although the decomposition

112
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:30,320
makes identification difficult,

113
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,680
a large number of maggots

114
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,210
have gathered at the wound.

115
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,120
A sharp weapon.

116
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,260
The killer used a sharp weapon

117
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,040
to stab the victim from behind,

118
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,970
causing multiple spleen injuries

119
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,340
and severe blood loss.

120
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,320
You were robbed.

121
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:58,960
My house

122
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:01,420
is so poor that all I have left are paintings.

123
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:02,980
A crime of passion.

124
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:04,680
Women

125
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,720
will only slow down my painting.

126
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,520
Then it's a vendetta.

127
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,700
It's true that quite a few people hate me.

128
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,920
Your painting is ready, sir.

129
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:30,880
Finally, the painting of beauties I've been waiting for.

130
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:37,380
This was brought back from the scene.

131
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,240
Judging by the traces,

132
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,240
it was made at the same time

133
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:43,240
as the portrait in Baoyue Pavilion.

134
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:46,560
Many identical scrolls were also hidden at the scene.

135
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,290
In addition,

136
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:50,240
there are some eunuchs' purchase records.

137
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:55,220
It seems samples were sent to the palace eunuchs first.

138
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:58,900
Eunuch Qin really knows how to create a gimmick.

139
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,480
Could it be that Jile Palace was exposed,

140
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,080
and Eunuch Qin silenced him?

141
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,360
But he clearly died before that.

142
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,460
Did he intend to kill beforehand?

143
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,560
Let's extract the fingerprints first.

144
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:13,880
Nonsense!

145
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,200
Qiuyue,

146
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,540
why are you being so mischievous?

147
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,400
I heard

148
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,440
you appointed Liu Chuan

149
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,520
as the coroner.

150
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,680
If this gets out,

151
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,730
people will laugh their heads off.

152
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,400
Another murder has occurred,

153
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,920
and it's highly likely related to Eunuch Qin.

154
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,280
How can I not investigate?

155
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,040
What?

156
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,440
Related to Eunuch Qin?

157
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:34,920
Then you definitely shouldn't touch it.

158
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,650
The Vice Minister has arrived.

159
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,000
I pay my respects, My Lord.

160
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,560
The murder case at Baoyue Pavilion

161
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,200
has alarmed the Ministry of Justice.

162
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:09,360
The Vice Minister has come specifically to investigate it.

163
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,280
Some people

164
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:12,040
should stop messing around,

165
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,360
to avoid humiliating themselves.

166
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:15,960
Vice Minister,

167
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:17,160
you grace us with your presence.

168
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,720
I apologize for not greeting you sooner.

169
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,400
Please forgive me, My Lord.

170
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:21,040
I am taking over this case.

171
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,080
My Lord.

172
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:26,160
Liu Chuan and I have already found crucial clues.

173
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,400
Not only did we discover the connection between the two murders,

174
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,200
but we are also very likely to find

175
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,240
evidence testifying against Eunuch Qin.

176
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,840
If we are not allowed to continue investigating this matter,

177
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,360
I am afraid it would be inappropriate.

178
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:34,880
Qiuyue,

179
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,559
do not be insolent in front of His Lordship.

180
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,080
My Lord.

181
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,720
Why won't you let me speak, My Lord?

182
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,560
Did you find any clues?

183
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:47,600
Liuchuan is about to extract the fingerprints from the scene.

184
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,460
Fingerprints?

185
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,680
You know how to investigate with fingerprints?

186
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:52,480
That's a piece of cake.

187
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:11,940
They match.

188
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,360
The fingerprints from both scenes

189
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,400
do have identical ones.

190
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,660
They match perfectly.

191
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,120
I'm exhausted.

192
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:20,560
M-

193
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:21,160
My Lord.

194
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:21,720
H-

195
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,720
He's playing you!

196
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,920
This is purely nonsense.

197
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:25,650
How dare you!

198
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:28,380
I studied investigation with my teacher

199
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,920
and learned about this.

200
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:32,410
Do you really think I know nothing?

201
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:35,020
If he was just scribbling from the start,

202
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:37,080
I would have taken him down already.

203
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,320
The Vice Minister's mentor?

204
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,240
Isn't that

205
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,600
the world-renowned

206
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,080
Prince Zhuoran?

207
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:47,320
It seems Zhuoran also knows about fingerprints.

208
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:48,760
Mr. Liu,

209
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:50,960
your fingerprint examination technique

210
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,490
is no less than my master's.

211
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:54,180
Who did you learn from?

212
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:58,010
Dijing Forensic Medical University.

213
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:58,840
You really come from the same school

214
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,960
as my master.

215
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,010
Greetings, Uncle-Master.

216
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,040
Get down to business.

217
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,680
I'm ready.

218
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,360
By the way, uncle,

219
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,760
I came here this time

220
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:40,960
not only to investigate

221
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:43,000
the scandal of eunuchs growing roots,

222
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,640
but also to collect evidence against Eunuch Qin.

223
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:47,680
Actually, regarding Eunuch Qin's deeds,

224
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,880
there have been rumors for a long time.

225
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:50,800
But he is backed by Consort De.

226
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,820
Can Consort De disregard the law?

227
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:54,920
So we must have solid evidence

228
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:56,880
to ensure nothing goes wrong.

229
00:11:58,280 --> 00:11:59,400
So what?

230
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:01,120
Who would back up a dead man?

231
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,240
Martial Uncle,

232
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:04,080
are you referring to Eunuch Qin?

233
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,320
But he's perfectly fine.

234
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:11,360
Do you have a split personality?

235
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:14,080
His days are numbered.

236
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:17,140
Stop keeping us in suspense and just tell us.

237
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:20,480
Based on Scholar Wang's fingerprints at the scene

238
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,840
and the time of death,

239
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:23,240
the ones who killed him

240
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:25,370
must be Eunuch Qiao and Eunuch Shuang.

241
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:46,760
After they took the scroll,

242
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:49,080
Eunuch Qiao killed Eunuch Shuang.

243
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:02,060
Then he was strangled to death by a third person.

244
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,650
I think the three of them

245
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,160
must be in cahoots.

246
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,160
Did they plan

247
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,280
to use this method

248
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,740
to expose the Jile Palace?

249
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,400
I think this is the first step.

250
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:12,480
They must know

251
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,640
that Eunuch Qin

252
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:14,760
is so powerful

253
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:17,120
that even if the Jile Palace is exposed,

254
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:19,050
he might not be brought to justice.

255
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:19,770
However,

256
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:20,880
it can alert the enemy

257
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:22,120
and draw Eunuch Qin into the trap.

258
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,920
What trap?

259
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:23,880
Growing roots

260
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:24,640
is the trap.

261
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:26,080
Can it really grow roots?

262
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,440
I didn't quite believe it either,

263
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,280
but the facts are right in front of us.

264
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:29,880
So,

265
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:30,720
we can only find the person

266
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,360
who made Eunuch Qiao grow roots

267
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,200
for an answer.

268
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,460
And who is that person?

269
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:40,290
The one who killed Eunuch Qiao was a woman.

270
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:44,240
But the first to mention growing roots was Axiu.

271
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:46,400
I think Axiu is the third person.
